1. *Čekala* je svoju zaručniku satima. (She waited for her fiancé for hours.) 
2. *Čekala* je na njega u parku. (She was waiting for him in the park.)
3. *Čekala* je da prođe kiša. (She was waiting for the rain to pass.)
4. *Čeka*la je da se vrati iz putovanja. (She was waiting for him to come back from his trip.)
5. *Čekao* je da sazna rezultate ispita. (He was waiting to find out the results of the exam.)
6. *Čekali* su da njihovi najbolji prijatelji dođu. (They were waiting for their best friends to come.)